elements.name: Automated User Homepage Visibility Validation
elements.description: Validating that Users that enter valid credentials and are logged in can see the planets and moons that they created on their dashboard. While Users who enter invalid credentials should not be able to reach the homepage.

steps.name: The user is on the login page at URL "http://localhost:8080/"
The user enters the username on the login page "Batman"
The user enters the password on the login page "I am the night"
The user clicks the login button
The user should be redirected to home page
